Mix together graham cracker crumbs, melted butter or margarine, and 1/4 cup white sugar. Pat mixture into the bottom of a 9 inch springform pan. A 9 x 13 inch pan may also be used. Prepare dream whip according to directions. Beat cream cheese with 1 cup white sugar and vanilla; beat until creamy. Fold Dream Whip (TM) into cream cheese mixture. Spread filling over crust. Refrigerate 1 to 2 hours, or until firm.